text: Juan de Dios Orozco was the 14th President (then called Supreme Director) of Nicaragua from 1 April to 31 May 1843. == See also == Category:Presidents of Nicaragua Category:Nicaraguan people of Basque descent Category:Year of death missing Category:Year of birth missing * Pablo Buitrago y Benavente * Manuel Pérez
title: Juan de Dios Orozco
